*     25.04.1991:  original (REVAD::BDK)
*     03.05.1991:  increase MAXACT to match SUBPAR limit (REVAD::BDK)
*     13.05.1991:  update comments (REVAD::BDK)
*     13.10.1992:  add DTASK__SYSNORM (RLVAD::AJC)
*    endhistory
